          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
            <div class="full-width-content">
            <Accordion variant='splitted' title="Fisher & Paykel Washer Repair FAQ">
              <AccordionItem title="How long does a Fisher & Paykel washer last?">
                <p>With proper care, most models last 10–15 years.</p>
              </AccordionItem>
              
              <AccordionItem title="Why is my Fisher & Paykel washer showing an error code 37?">
                <p>This code often indicates a pump blockage or failure.</p>
              </AccordionItem>
              
              <AccordionItem title="Can you repair older SmartDrive washers?">
                <p>Yes — as long as parts are available, we can service both older and newer SmartDrive models.</p>
              </AccordionItem>
              
              <AccordionItem title="Is it worth repairing my Fisher & Paykel washer?">
                <p>For most units under 10 years old, repair is typically the best long-term value.</p>
              </AccordionItem>
            </Accordion>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="page-container" id="anchor-9">
        <div class="header-container">
          <div class="head-content-h">
            <h2>Service Areas</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
          <div class="full-width-content">
            <p style="margin-top: 10px;">Same Day Appliance Repair serves:</p>
            <ul >
              <li><strong>Los Angeles</strong> <a href="/" class="underline font-bold" style="color: #dc2626 !important;">(see LA Service Hub)</a></li>
              <li><strong>Orange County</strong></li>
              <li><strong>Ventura County</strong></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="page-container" id="anchor-10">
        <div class="header-container">
          <div class="head-content-h">
            <h2>Call Now for Fisher & Paykel Repair</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
          <div class="full-width-content">
            <p>We service <strong>Los Angeles, Pasadena, Santa Monica, Glendale, Burbank, Irvine, Anaheim, Long Beach</strong>, and nearby cities. Schedule your appointment at <a href="/" class="underline font-bold" style="color: #dc2626 !important;">samedayappliance.repair</a> or call <strong>(323) 870-4790</strong> now.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="page-container" id="anchor-11">
        <div class="header-container">
          <div class="head-content-h">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
          <div class="full-width-content">
            <p style="margin-top: 5px;">Same Day Appliance Repair is Southern California's <strong>A+ rated, BBB-accredited</strong> team for residential and commercial washer service. Our licensed, factory-trained technicians work with OEM parts and follow brand-specific manuals to ensure accurate repairs. With same-day service and a 90-day warranty, we're your trusted partner for Fisher & Paykel appliance repair in the Los Angeles area.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-section">
        <Contactbtn />
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
 
